data.description: Welcome to this stunning 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home with a pool, offering almost 2300 square feet of living space. Situated on a spacious cul-de-sac lot, this home boasts beautiful curb appeal and a well-maintained exterior with recently painted trim. Step inside and be greeted by an open floor plan, featuring formal living and dining spaces that are perfect for entertaining. The kitchen is a chef's dream, with granite countertops, a custom backsplash, stainless steel appliances, built-in oven/microwave, wood cabinets, a large island, and a breakfast bar. Cooking will be a breeze with the gas cooktop. The owner's suite is spacious and offers an ensuite bath with a large walk-in tiled shower and a separate soaking tub providing a luxurious retreat. Enjoy the Florida weather in the pavered, screened-in lanai surrounding the sparkling pool. The pool is a saltwater pool and features a multi-color light system that can be selected on a rotation system or a single color. The pool area also has a wireless speaker system, creating the perfect ambiance for outdoor gatherings. This home is equipped with a whole house security system, including audio and video surveillance. Motion sensor lights are installed in the rear corners of the house and over the garage, ensuring added safety and security. The garage itself is built deeper, providing extra space, and has a cut-in for a work desk in the right back corner, which also gives access to tub plumbing. The windows in the house are polarized and hurricane strength, offering both protection and energy efficiency. The attic has a heat barrier that was installed during construction, helping to keep the home cool in the summer. Other notable features of this home include a low-E garage door, a sprinkler system with rain auto shutoff, a tankless water heater that has been serviced annually, and a 5-year-old roof. The driveway and lanai have been sealed, adding to the overall maintenance of the property.  For added convenience, gas lines have been installed outside, allowing for the possibility of adding an outdoor kitchen and fire pits beyond the pool area as well as electrical and water connections for outdoor kitchen have also been added. This home is truly a gem, with its upgraded features, meticulous maintenance, and desirable location. Hunter Douglas custom Luminets and Silhouette window coverings throughout the home as well.  Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours!
